data.title: List of Books
data.meta_description: List of Books - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document appears to be a file listing showing the filenames, sizes, and file types of various ebooks stored in a Kindle library folder sorted from A-C. There are over 200 files listed ranging in size from 144 KB to 12 MB. The files cover a wide variety of genres and authors, including fiction from Douglas Adams, Richard Adams, Louisa May Alcott, and Lloyd Alexander, as well as non-fiction from Madeleine Albright, Arthur Agatston, and Liaquat Ahamed among many others.
